{"tid":999182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好嬲，成日俾人屈精神病","createTime":"2019-01-28T13:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T13:58:23.000Z","uid":64601,"like":154,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"56ff5ca061787387ee60789f19884d72b98e8730","tid":999182,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日去見工，咁咪填下form，見佢問我status，我咪寫返whatsapp句點擊此處與型男展開激情對話，個hr見到大大聲屌我，話：叫你填婚姻狀況呀！咁我咪寫A0。佢睇完好撚嬲，仲話我：你痴線㗎？有精神病睇醫生啦。<br />\n<br />\n我一巴星落去，話：我中度弱智㗎！你就精神病。然後好似大力得濟打到佢腦震盪，仲搞到佢精神分裂。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲知點先醫得返佢？佢而家出咗個半歲細路人格出嚟係咁奶我粒lin，好撚痕，有冇人幫到我？"},{"pid":"7f0493f6d4ed729ff61c8e75db3263013069aee0","tid":999182,"uid":18485,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"中立非青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9930a7dacf7550832cb627649ccf008c6e17310f","tid":999182,"uid":64601,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"粒lin而家俾佢奶到濕哂，係咪會做暴乳類動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7f4d8092861772d57683a82aa8517de6be2cd4","tid":999182,"uid":47614,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"3ad1997b2bb42489dd374040f0ff70b61f3fd1ab","tid":999182,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f0493f6d4ed729ff61c8e75db3263013069aee0","tid":999182,"uid":18485,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"中立非青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"再講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最多攬炒"},{"pid":"1f42b605f16307277769eae5e5732a2265f2f120","tid":999182,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28